Description: An extended, maintained fork of the Fjelstul World Cup Database.
    Contains 27 datasets covering all aspects of the FIFA World Cup, including
    matches, teams, players, managers, referees, squads, goals, penalty kicks,
    bookings, substitutions, standings, and awards. It covers all 22 men's
    tournaments (1930-2022) and all 8 women's tournaments (1991-2019). Original
    database by Joshua C. Fjelstul, Ph.D. (https://github.com/jfjelstul/worldcup),
    used under CC-BY-SA 4.0. Extended and maintained by Sadanand Venkataraman.
    A companion Python package builds a forecasting and analytics layer on top
    of this core data; see
    https://github.com/sadanandv/fifa-worldcup-data-python.
URL: https://github.com/sadanandv/fifa-worldcup-data
